<br>
Consideration is defined as something of value, often times money or property. <br>
<br>
In the case of a Social Contract.....what do individuals have to &quot;give&quot; as consideration if not a partial grant of their individual liberties and rights which they possessed prior to the contract formation? <br>
<br>
If the rights do not exist until the contract in formed(Raolf's position), then what did individuals &quot;give&quot; to the gov't as consideration?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dmhcas>dmhcas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 119<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/23/03 1:50:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for the Libertarians</span><hr size=1> I'm going to the frig and get some shine. I gotta stop my head from hurting. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raolfcq>RaolfCQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I Live Here</span><br>  Posts: 1070<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/23/03 4:25:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=22>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for the Libertarians</span><hr size=1> Their word.  I think bare agreement to abide by soemthing has value. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=truthreason>TruthReason</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I'm actually Goanad.</span><br>  Posts: 1064<br>